author: Ovid
message: Take rest; a field that has rested gives a bountiful crop.
title: Thought of the day

author: Anais Nin
message: Age does not protect you from love. But love, to some extent, protects you from age.
title: Thought of the day

author: Forrest Church
message: Do what you can. Want what you have. Be who you are.
title: Thought of the day

author: Coco Chanel
message: There are people who have money and people who are rich.
title: Thought of the day
